definition.value: A 2-hydroxy carboxylate that is the conjugate base of 3-(indol-3-yl)lactic acid.
A phosphatidylinositol 3-phosphate in which the inositol moiety is the D-myo-isomer.
A ribose monophosphate having the phosphate group at the 5-position and an amino group in place of hydroxy at the anomeric centre.
